snippet.title: outsidexbox
snippet.description:
Daily videos from Outside Xbox about Xbox Series X, Xbox One and several things that aren't Xbox. A new list every Thursday and Show of the Week every Friday! 

Join Outside Xbox hosts Andy Farrant, Mike Channell and Jane Douglas for gameplay, shows, previews, tips, and much (some) more. Also, find them in yet more videos on Outside Xbox companion channel Outside Xtra: http://www.youtube.com/outsidextra
